												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "She already mentioned she had a bad feeling about this lady. Turns out she was right - she serves a devil called Mammon. Karlach isn't pleased about this but is glad she was right. Slightly comic, like she's expecting someone to challenge the fact that she knew it was Mammon (like saying 'I knew it!' after hearing an answer on jeopardy)."
												}
